description: Try our easy to follow Baked Turkey Rolls Filled With Chestnuts & Mushrooms recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Baked Turkey Rolls Filled With Chestnuts & Mushrooms
name: Baked Turkey Rolls Filled With Chestnuts & Mushrooms Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place 1 tablespoon of the mixture on each turkey strip and carefully roll it up. Place the rolls join-down in a baking dish, making sure they are quite tightly packed. Drizzle over the remaining olive oil, cover with foil, and bake in the oven for 30 minutes. Remove the foil and cook for a further 10 minutes, or until brown. Serve with a crisp green salad.
